// Palette notes for the active niri modules.
//
// niri accepts only one top-level `layout {}` node, so these color values must
// live inside their owning modules instead of being included as a second layout.
// Current active color values are in:
// - dms/layout.kdl: layout background, focus ring, border, shadow, tab indicator, insert hint
// - dms/alttab.kdl: recent window highlight
